    "body": "Previous package version didn't select proper optimization for CPUs with AVX512. This PR adds auto-selection of AVX-512 optimization for some supported CPUs (tested on skylake-x, newer CPU should work too).\r\n\r\nAlso added  2.15a1 version with implement another AVX512 optimization algorithm. This gives about 2.5 times performance improvement other generic build (i.e. previous spack install namd%intel)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n-Nikolay\r\n\r\n",
